                "name": "Splatter",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "As a standard action, a putrid ooze can throw a portion of its acidic sludge at a creature within 30 feet. The putrid ooze must make a successful ranged touch attack to hit the target. Creatures struck take 10d6 points of acid damage."
